  "description": {
    "zh": "你来的真是时候，伙计！我记得你帮我搞定过郊区的监视项目。\n\n现在化工厂有着不小的骚动，我打赌你肯定听说了！作为真正的朋友，帮我安插一点眼线没有问题吧？\n\n我看到那里有一些起重机，那可是绝佳的监视位置。好了，行动起来吧。",
    "en": "You got here just in time, man! I remember you helped me a hell of a lot with surveillance in the suburbs. \n\nAnd now there's all this commotion at the chemical plant, I bet you're well aware of it! Be a true pal, arrange some eyes for me there too, yea?\n\nI've seen some cranes there, they would be a perfect place for a camera. Alright, chop chop."
  },
